3. Third-party Services:
We may engage third-party service providers to assist in delivering our services. These providers are carefully vetted to ensure compliance with our privacy and security standards. Your Personal Information is shared with third parties only as necessary to provide the requested service.
4. Data Ownership and Security:
You retain ownership of the data entered or provided by you in SmartBusiness. We take measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. We recommend safeguarding your account credentials and promptly reporting any suspected security breaches.
5. User Rights:
You have the right to access, modify, or delete your Personal Information stored in SmartBusiness.
